, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": 2934729, "tag": null, "text": "只有民主才能战胜历史周期律", "timestamp": 1636869116, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2934859, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": 2934735, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 机械历史观不值一驳。数风流人物，还看今朝。", "timestamp": 1636869149, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2934884, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": 2934832, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 永远会有朱姓亲王，八旗子弟，red后代这些寄生虫", "timestamp": 1636869321, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2934921, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": 2934884, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 一个社会特权阶级是难免的，但如果制度设计的好可以减少他们的影响，让大部分人也能正常的生产和贸易。但感觉中国集权了上千年，这种裙带关系的影响太大了，不走自由化改革就只能向当今圣上这样强力反腐、同时还要监督他们不能懒政怠政，至少从现在来看困难重重。", "timestamp": 1636869551, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2936193, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么不分析大汉", "timestamp": 1636879181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2938519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": 2936193, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 先射箭再画靶子呗", "timestamp": 1636894151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2939454, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "胆子真大", "timestamp": 1636900339, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2940930, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大胆！", "timestamp": 1636909269, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2942712, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "狂！", "timestamp": 1636943999, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2945246, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大明一代目是过江前后的两批勋臣掐架，顺便被一代目一锅端了（", "timestamp": 1636963180, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2945646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 557810, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哈人", "timestamp": 1636966523, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 40, "pid": 557810, "reply": 20, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "大明一代目虽然诛尽开国元勋，但是整顿了吏治，避免了贪腐之风自由化的趋势；\n大唐和大明的二代目虽然都得位不正，但是在位期间国家强盛，建功立业，奠定基础；\n大汉和大明的三四代目韬光养晦，闷声发大财，百姓富足，文景之治和仁宣之治使国库充盈；\n然而大明五代目猪骑朕却听信谗言，独断专权，好大喜功，土木堡之变竟将大明百年积攒之国力一朝耗尽。如此无能却又权力欲极重，趁朱祁钰病重之际发动夺门之变，成为史上唯一一个两次登基延续任期的皇帝，我大明国运由此盛极转衰。", "timestamp": 1636867377, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636966525, "url": "", "vote": {}}}